des:
You can use the Law Office Of Michael J. George voice application to ask questions about Law Office Of Michael J. George has been aggressively doing battle for his clients for over 25 years and knows what it takes to get you where you need to go in your case.

After the Welcome Message, here are some questions you can ask:

- "What are your business hours?"
- "What's your address?"
- "Tell me more about the business."
- "What services do you offer?"
- "What payments do you accept?"

And more!
